# Implement Transaction Service

## Description

This PR implements the transaction service which allows users to record their financial transactions. The service includes endpoints for creating and retrieving transactions.

## Changes

- Added `transactionService.js` with endpoints for creating and retrieving transactions.
- Set up MongoDB connection and defined the transaction schema.

## How to Test

1. Run the transaction service using `node transactionService.js`.
2. Use Postman or a similar tool to send POST and GET requests to the service endpoints.

